{"type": "article", "id": 12898, "title": "谁说时尚内容不赚钱，以及，Tory Burch发了运动新品 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2015-07-31T14:20:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13819, "name": "运动套装"}, {"id": 993, "name": "高跟鞋"}, {"id": 13820, "name": "邮差包"}, {"id": 9968, "name": "手机壳"}, {"id": 4221, "name": "WSJ"}, {"id": 329, "name": "宝洁"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 11593, "name": "Yoox"}, {"id": 2882, "name": "Tory Burch"}, {"id": 1817, "name": "纪梵希"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052208054ot1UmkFyOaTENAH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h4>\r\n\t一些重要的新闻：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2015/07/t-wsj-magazine-september-ad-pages\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>《华尔街日报》（WSJ）和 </strong><em><strong>T </strong></em><strong>的 9 月刊广告页数打破以往记录</strong></a><strong> </strong><strong>|</strong> 前者广告有 100.4 页，同比增长 10%，32% 为秋季时装广告，新广告客户中有 9% 为时尚奢侈品牌；而 <em>T Magazine </em>广告有 165 页，同比增长 4%，并拥有 12 个新广告客户，其中包括 Stuart Weitzman，Kenzo，J Brand 和 Marni. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/mass/p-and-g-sees-80-drop-in-profits-beauty-sales-slide10194861-10194861/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>宝洁净收入下跌 80%</strong></a> <strong>| </strong>宝洁公司周四发布财报，第四季度净收入从去年同期的 25.8亿美元下降 80% 至 5.21 亿美元。净销售额在截至 6 月 30 日的三个月中下跌了9.2％，至 177.9 亿，只有有机系列上涨了 1 个百分点。这和此前将旗下四十余个品牌出售给 Coty 有关。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/avon-reports-net-profit-gains-51-6-for-2nd-quarter-10194986/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>雅芳二季度净收入上涨</strong></a><strong> | </strong>雅芳周四财报中，其第二季度净收益与去年同期（1900 万美元）相比上涨了 51.6%  至 2880 万美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2015/7/30/9074243/cos-expansio\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>H&amp;M </strong><strong>的姊妹品牌 COS 预计至年底开至 27 家店</strong></a> <strong>|</strong><strong> </strong>相较 H&amp;M，COS 走极简、高档路线，吸引到一众追求质量的人群。COS 会根据各地区网上销售情况，继续在纽约和洛杉矶开新店，年底完成美国以外的 23 家门店。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/07/27/artemis-ponant-idUSL5N1073JO20150727\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>皮诺家族旗下公司 Artémis 参股豪华游艇制造商枫丹白露</strong></a><strong> | </strong>继宣布收购法国最大豪华游轮经营商 Compagnie Du Ponant 庞洛游轮的计划后，法国奢侈品集团 Kering SA (KER.PA) 开云集团背后的 Pinault 家族再次通过旗下家族控股公司 Artémis SA 间接入股法国豪华游艇制造商 Fountaine Pajot SA (ALFPC.PA) 枫丹白露。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/yoox-profits-surge-10195152/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>意大利时尚电商 Yoox 上半年利润大增</strong></a><strong> </strong><strong>| </strong>Yoox 昨日宣布上半年调整后净利润上涨了38.3% 至 440 万美元。企业发展和财经传播总监 Silvia Scagnelli 表示 “Yoox 在中国风头正劲，呈两位数涨势，并提供了巨大潜力和机会。尤其是作为合并集团之后更是如此（今年 3 月宣布与 Net-a-Porter 合并）”\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t一些值得一看的：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/31/fashion/tory-burchs-new-tory-sport-line-first-look.html?_r=1\" target=\"_blank\">Tory Burch 运动线新品预览</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/31/fashion/tory-burchs-new-tory-sport-line-first-look.html?_r=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220757GhbBWNUFR52zpvtm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72141707\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/31/fashion/tory-burchs-new-tory-sport-line-first-look.html?_r=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220758EZuahS0xMJWH5wz4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51724138\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t高端科技健身装备公司 Isaora，与韩裔设计师 Siki Im 在纽约创立的品牌 DEN IM 联手推出 <a href=\"http://www.gq.com/story/isaora-den-im-siki-im-collab\" target=\"_blank\">2015 “RVN”</a><a href=\"http://www.gq.com/story/isaora-den-im-siki-im-collab\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><a href=\"http://www.gq.com/story/isaora-den-im-siki-im-collab\" target=\"_blank\">夏季限量版套装系列</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220758A1SiYk4ahxZ2CHvz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81292517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140606534qcpBQTKmHXkY2.jpg\" width=\"731\" height=\"454\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62106703\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220759kryvaB4WnJV1jfcd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://qz.com/468268/this-instagram-celebritys-filter-free-life-is-refreshingly-authentic/\" target=\"_blank\">这个 Instagram 上很火的明星是个塑料小人</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://qz.com/468268/this-instagram-celebritys-filter-free-life-is-refreshingly-authentic/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052207591oq0OxpRJzjlmhSt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6359743\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://qz.com/468268/this-instagram-celebritys-filter-free-life-is-refreshingly-authentic/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220800cMqueR0WQhasK5FI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67573696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://qz.com/468268/this-instagram-celebritys-filter-free-life-is-refreshingly-authentic/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220800Fcxw6IgXOU8WRP0L.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58834951\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2015/7/givenchy-rider-bag\" target=\"_blank\"><span></span>纪梵希发布 2015 秋季新款背包和邮差包</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2015/7/givenchy-rider-bag\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220801ThX23tzV7ZnSu1Os.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66924266\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2015/7/givenchy-rider-bag\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220801SvWNzqmPnAUguREw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.844\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2015/7/givenchy-rider-bag\" target=\"_blank\"><span> </span> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<span></span></a> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/features/sandra-bullocks-minionsinspired-shoes-raise-84850-for-charity-10387912.html\" target=\"_blank\">桑德拉·布洛克拍卖小黄人高跟鞋</a>，<span>为 C</span>harity Art\r\n+ Practice <span>共筹集 42</span>425 美元。这双是由好莱坞极受欢迎的鞋履品牌 Rupert Sanderson 为其定制，她曾穿着出席小黄人首映，<span> </span>每双都有亲笔签名。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052208010PsoRGHwx2UJOv5h.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74446337\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/designer-iphone-6-cases-buy/\" target=\"_blank\">Moschino、Marc by\r\nMarc Jacobs<span> </span>以及<span> Kate Spade<span> </span></span><span>设计的 </span><span>iPhone 6 </span></a><span><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/designer-iphone-6-cases-buy/\" target=\"_blank\">手机壳</a> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/designer-iphone-6-cases-buy/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220802g7x8uoH46azJRZhY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75046904\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Moschino Spray Can，115 美元 &amp; Kate spade new york Eat Cake，45 美元</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220802aHN8kgtnjMAW3qUV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75046904\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Tory Burch，65 美元 &amp; Marc by Marc Jacobs Gold Foil，38 美元</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t一些有意思的说法：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t一个猜测，全红色 Sneaker 会成为潮流？各大品牌都发布了全红配色的运动鞋款。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220803iHDIFu7m3Rwa4jOn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6023166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Asics GEL-Lyte V</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220803cUjyz7Ks8bn9mxl5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60806452\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Saint Laurent SL 01</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220804z0fkKrFIsQU17dxH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55341506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Air Jordan 11LAB4 </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220804FNhkIK5U0J1adrvG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55298651\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<span><em>                                               NIKE DUNK CMFT PRM</em></span><span><em> </em></span>\n\n\n\n"}